snippet.title: NerdOut!
snippet.description:
Welcome to NerdOut! Music. 

We strive to bring you the greatest tunes about all things geek. Video games, movies and pop culture mixed with modern rock and hip hop. We are NerdOut! and we love what we do. 
Subscribe today and join all the fun!

Please DO NOT upload our music to without permission. This is to protect the integrity of our channel.
We hope you understand.

NerdOut is: The8thHawk, NemRaps, and Ben Schuller
